These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, house
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of house##1
2. the fan of house is not to the right of the fan of house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | house | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, action
1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, hamster
1. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
2. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | goat | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, boat
1. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | bike | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | gardening | skydiving |

 #################################

 
